ActDivorce Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Central Registry of Divorce Proceedings Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the CENTRAL REGISTRY OF DIVORCE PROCEEDINGS REGULATIONS to allow the Central Registry of Divorce Proceedings to presume that a divorce proceeding is discontinued where Part II of the Divorce Proceedings Form is not received within six years after the notification referred to in subsection 5(3) of the Regulations was sent.
